The use of probabilistic methods and the Erdős-Lovasz-Spencer theorem suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the field of probabilistic combinatorics (cs.GT). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of algorithms and computational complexity, which are topics covered in the sub-categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
